{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1040,"text":"I'm here to offer you\na new way to think about my field,"},{"time":4815,"text":"artificial intelligence."},{"time":6607,"text":"I think the purpose of AI"},{"time":8645,"text":"is to empower humans\nwith machine intelligence."},{"time":13286,"text":"And as machines get smarter,"},{"time":15760,"text":"we get smarter."},{"time":17907,"text":"I call this \"humanistic AI\" --"},{"time":20443,"text":"artificial intelligence\ndesigned to meet human needs"},{"time":24138,"text":"by collaborating and augmenting people."},{"time":28149,"text":"Now, today I'm happy to see"},{"time":30083,"text":"that the idea of an intelligent assistant"},{"time":32284,"text":"is mainstream."},{"time":33777,"text":"It's the well-accepted metaphor\nfor the interface between humans and AI."},{"time":39556,"text":"And the one I helped create\nis called Siri."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42957,"text":"You know Siri."},{"time":44133,"text":"Siri is the thing that knows your intent"},{"time":46802,"text":"and helps you do it for you,"},{"time":48868,"text":"helps you get things done."},{"time":50393,"text":"But what you might not know\nis that we designed Siri"},{"time":53645,"text":"as humanistic AI,"},{"time":55635,"text":"to augment people\nwith a conversational interface"},{"time":58830,"text":"that made it possible for them\nto use mobile computing,"},{"time":62307,"text":"regardless of who they were\nand their abilities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66814,"text":"Now for most of us,"},{"time":68415,"text":"the impact of this technology"},{"time":71220,"text":"is to make things\na little bit easier to use."},{"time":73916,"text":"But for my friend Daniel,"},{"time":77352,"text":"the impact of the AI\nin these systems is a life changer."},{"time":81217,"text":"You see, Daniel is a really social guy,"},{"time":86074,"text":"and he's blind and quadriplegic,"},{"time":88614,"text":"which makes it hard to use those devices\nthat we all take for granted."},{"time":92497,"text":"The last time I was at his house,\nhis brother said,"},{"time":94963,"text":"\"Hang on a second, Daniel's not ready."},{"time":96845,"text":"He's on the phone with a woman\nhe met online.\""},{"time":100250,"text":"I'm like, \"That's cool, how'd he do it?\""},{"time":102284,"text":"Well, Daniel uses Siri\nto manage his own social life --"},{"time":106731,"text":"his email, text and phone --"},{"time":108695,"text":"without depending on his caregivers."},{"time":112501,"text":"This is kind of interesting, right?"},{"time":114263,"text":"The irony here is great."},{"time":115604,"text":"Here's the man whose relationship with AI"},{"time":118524,"text":"helps him have relationships\nwith genuine human beings."},{"time":122805,"text":"And this is humanistic AI."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127404,"text":"Another example with\nlife-changing consequences"},{"time":129826,"text":"is diagnosing cancer."},{"time":132795,"text":"When a doctor suspects cancer,"},{"time":134974,"text":"they take a sample\nand send it to a pathologist,"},{"time":137701,"text":"who looks at it under a microscope."},{"time":140145,"text":"Now, pathologists look at\nhundreds of slides"},{"time":142694,"text":"and millions of cells every day."},{"time":145630,"text":"So to support this task,"},{"time":147041,"text":"some researchers made an AI classifier."},{"time":151548,"text":"Now, the classifier says,\n\"Is this cancer or is this not cancer?\""},{"time":156125,"text":"looking at the pictures."},{"time":158355,"text":"The classifier was pretty good,"},{"time":160967,"text":"but not as good as the person,"},{"time":163945,"text":"who got it right most of the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166427,"text":"But when they combine the ability\nof the machine and the human together,"},{"time":172631,"text":"accuracy went to 99.5 percent."},{"time":177150,"text":"Adding that AI to a partnership\neliminated 85 percent of the errors"},{"time":182175,"text":"that the human pathologist\nwould have made working alone."},{"time":186820,"text":"That's a lot of cancer\nthat would have otherwise gone untreated."},{"time":191097,"text":"Now, for the curious, it turns out"},{"time":193051,"text":"that the human was better\nat rejecting false positives,"},{"time":196549,"text":"and the machine was better\nat recognizing those hard-to-spot cases."},{"time":200145,"text":"But the lesson here isn't about\nwhich agent is better"},{"time":203406,"text":"at this image-classification task."},{"time":205888,"text":"Those things are changing every day."},{"time":207751,"text":"The lesson here"},{"time":209343,"text":"is that by combining the abilities\nof the human and machine,"},{"time":212727,"text":"it created a partnership\nthat had superhuman performance."},{"time":218543,"text":"And that is humanistic AI."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222787,"text":"Now let's look at another example"},{"time":224797,"text":"with turbocharging performance."},{"time":227108,"text":"This is design."},{"time":228535,"text":"Now, let's say you're an engineer."},{"time":230600,"text":"You want to design\na new frame for a drone."},{"time":232741,"text":"You get out your favorite\nsoftware tools, CAD tools,"},{"time":235829,"text":"and you enter the form and the materials,\nand then you analyze performance."},{"time":240068,"text":"That gives you one design."},{"time":242162,"text":"If you give those same tools to an AI,"},{"time":245863,"text":"it can generate thousands of designs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250193,"text":"This video by Autodesk is amazing."},{"time":252151,"text":"This is real stuff."},{"time":254092,"text":"So this transforms how we do design."},{"time":257187,"text":"The human engineer now"},{"time":258639,"text":"says what the design should achieve,"},{"time":261978,"text":"and the machine says,"},{"time":263158,"text":"\"Here's the possibilities.\""},{"time":265758,"text":"Now in her job, the engineer's job"},{"time":268722,"text":"is to pick the one that best meets\nthe goals of the design,"},{"time":271846,"text":"which she knows as a human\nbetter than anyone else,"},{"time":275209,"text":"using human judgment and expertise."},{"time":277414,"text":"In this case, the winning form"},{"time":279018,"text":"looks kind of like something\nnature would have designed,"},{"time":281753,"text":"minus a few million years of evolution"},{"time":283892,"text":"and all that unnecessary fur."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288424,"text":"Now let's see where this idea\nof humanistic AI might lead us"},{"time":293120,"text":"if we follow it into\nthe speculative beyond."},{"time":296118,"text":"What's a kind of augmentation\nthat we would all like to have?"},{"time":299529,"text":"Well, how about cognitive enhancement?"},{"time":303904,"text":"Instead of asking,"},{"time":305407,"text":"\"How smart can we make our machines?\""},{"time":307492,"text":"let's ask"},{"time":308689,"text":"\"How smart can our machines make us?\""},{"time":313105,"text":"I mean, take memory for example."},{"time":315511,"text":"Memory is the foundation\nof human intelligence."},{"time":319767,"text":"But human memory is famously flawed."},{"time":323541,"text":"We're great at telling stories,"},{"time":325639,"text":"but not getting the details right."},{"time":327614,"text":"And our memories -- they decay over time."},{"time":330844,"text":"I mean, like, where did the '60s go,\nand can I go there, too?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":334100,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":336648,"text":"But what if you could have a memory\nthat was as good as computer memory,"},{"time":342158,"text":"and was about your life?"},{"time":345714,"text":"What if you could remember\nevery person you ever met,"},{"time":348527,"text":"how to pronounce their name,"},{"time":350497,"text":"their family details,\ntheir favorite sports,"},{"time":352613,"text":"the last conversation you had with them?"},{"time":354600,"text":"If you had this memory all your life,"},{"time":357279,"text":"you could have the AI look\nat all the interactions"},{"time":360601,"text":"you had with people over time"},{"time":362042,"text":"and help you reflect on the long arc\nof your relationships."},{"time":366530,"text":"What if you could have the AI read\neverything you've ever read"},{"time":371620,"text":"and listen to every song\nyou've ever heard?"},{"time":375344,"text":"From the tiniest clue,\nit could help you retrieve"},{"time":379107,"text":"anything you've ever seen or heard before."},{"time":381931,"text":"Imagine what that would do\nfor the ability to make new connections"},{"time":385205,"text":"and form new ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386809,"text":"And what about our bodies?"},{"time":389732,"text":"What if we could remember the consequences\nof every food we eat,"},{"time":394034,"text":"every pill we take,"},{"time":396485,"text":"every all-nighter we pull?"},{"time":399048,"text":"We could do our own science\non our own data"},{"time":401782,"text":"about what makes us feel\ngood and stay healthy."},{"time":405666,"text":"And imagine how this could revolutionize"},{"time":408166,"text":"the way we manage\nallergies and chronic disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412909,"text":"I believe that AI will make\npersonal memory enhancement a reality."},{"time":419122,"text":"I can't say when or what\nform factors are involved,"},{"time":422627,"text":"but I think it's inevitable,"},{"time":425923,"text":"because the very things\nthat make AI successful today --"},{"time":430774,"text":"the availability of comprehensive data"},{"time":433291,"text":"and the ability for machines\nto make sense of that data --"},{"time":436863,"text":"can be applied to the data of our lives."},{"time":440505,"text":"And those data are here today,\navailable for all of us,"},{"time":444016,"text":"because we lead digitally mediated lives,"},{"time":448570,"text":"in mobile and online."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451833,"text":"In my view, a personal memory\nis a private memory."},{"time":455747,"text":"We get to choose what is and is not\nrecalled and retained."},{"time":460517,"text":"It's absolutely essential\nthat this be kept very secure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465294,"text":"Now for most of us,"},{"time":466780,"text":"the impact of augmented personal memory"},{"time":469697,"text":"will be a more improved mental gain,"},{"time":472456,"text":"maybe, hopefully, a bit more social grace."},{"time":476658,"text":"But for the millions who suffer\nfrom Alzheimer's and dementia,"},{"time":483209,"text":"the difference that augmented\nmemory could make"},{"time":485436,"text":"is a difference\nbetween a life of isolation"},{"time":489016,"text":"and a life of dignity and connection."}]},{"cues":[{"time":492166,"text":"We are in the middle of a renaissance\nin artificial intelligence right now."},{"time":498652,"text":"I mean, in just the past few years,"},{"time":500647,"text":"we're beginning to see\nsolutions to AI problems"},{"time":504302,"text":"that we have struggled\nwith literally for decades:"},{"time":509226,"text":"speech understanding, text understanding,"},{"time":511917,"text":"image understanding."},{"time":514177,"text":"We have a choice in how we use\nthis powerful technology."},{"time":519268,"text":"We can choose to use AI\nto automate and compete with us,"},{"time":524156,"text":"or we can use AI to augment\nand collaborate with us,"},{"time":528157,"text":"to overcome our cognitive limitations"},{"time":531252,"text":"and to help us do what we want to do,"},{"time":534438,"text":"only better."},{"time":536339,"text":"And as we discover new ways\nto give machines intelligence,"},{"time":542867,"text":"we can distribute that intelligence"},{"time":545960,"text":"to all of the AI assistants in the world,"},{"time":548365,"text":"and therefore to every person,\nregardless of circumstance."},{"time":553189,"text":"And that is why,"},{"time":554742,"text":"every time a machine gets smarter,"},{"time":558628,"text":"we get smarter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561028,"text":"That is an AI worth spreading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":564785,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565991,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}